Package gov.nasa.ial.mde.util

Provides MDE utility classes.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Comparison The Comparison interface allows for objects to be compared.
 

Class Summary
ArrayUtil The ArrayUtil class is a utility class for arrays.
ByteArray The ByteArray class represents a variable length array of bytes that automatically grows in capacity as needed to hold the added data.
LocalResourceResolver This resolver will load the given URI from the class path, which the file could be in either a Jar file or in a directory.
MathUtil MathUtil is a math utility class.
PointsUtil PointsUtil is utility class for handling the PointXY and MultiPointXY classes.
QSorter A quick sort class.
ResourceUtil A utility for loading resources files, which could be located in a Jar file.
SortedKeyStrings The SortedKeyStrings class creates a sorted array of string keys from a given Hashtable.
StringSplitter The StringSplitter class splits a String into an array of Strings based on the splitting string.
TrailUtil The TrailUtil class is a utility for handling point trails.
